Package org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.safra

Class SafraContainment

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractAlgorithm
org.svvrl.goal.core.comp.safra.SafraContainment
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.EventListener, Algorithm, AlgorithmListener, Containment<FSA,​FSA,​InputSequence>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ModifiedSafraContainment
public class SafraContainment
extends AbstractAlgorithm
implements Containment<FSA,​FSA,​InputSequence>
Test if an NBW A is contained in another NBW B by constructing the intersection of A and the complement of B incrementally. The complement of B is based on Safra's construction.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
